posts.post_title: FT:  T206 McCauley PSA 2 with a brown Hindu back
posts.post_content:

Heinie Berger

Mordecai Brown portrait
Al Burch fielding
Donie Bush
Ross Helm
Ernie Howard
Harry Pattee horizontal
Barney Pelty horizontal
Ed Reagan
Woodie Thornton

Looking to trade for cards graded PSA 2, 3, or 4.  Please PM if you have anything in my wheelhouse!

Marty
